| 
| Definition of a simple class, i.e. a class that has no generic parameters and is 1:1 with
| the type it generates.
| 

class BMM_SIMPLE_CLASS
    is_a BMM_CLASS

feature_group ("access")

    | 
    | Generate a type object that represents the type of this class. Can only be an instance of
    | `BMM_SIMPLE_TYPE` or a descendant.
    | 
    func type:BMM_SIMPLE_TYPE
        ;


end
